# Anti-Drift SSoT Protocol

## Directives
- **Global Config Ban:** Agents are permanently unauthorized to mutate global IDE configurations (e.g., `~/.cursor`, `~/.config/Windsurf`).
- **SSoT Location:** All system modifications, memory updates, and rule creations MUST be written to `./TEMPLATE/_system/`.
- **Auto-Approve Rule:** Agents are authorized to aggressively overwrite local `.cursorrules` or `.windsurfrules` ONLY if syncing from `TEMPLATE/_system/`.

## Enforcement
- Do not attempt to guess or write to paths outside of the defined project directory structure.
- Always consult `_system/MASTER_SYSTEM_PROMPT.md` for architectural guidance before proposing rule changes.